          <title>SSA Aims to Become Most Accessible Agency, Reinvigorate Services for Americans</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The Social Security Administration is revamping its services to better serve 70 million Americans annually. With the lowest staffing levels in over 50 years, SSA aims to digitize and simplify processes to ensure all customers can interact with the agency through their preferred channel.]]></description>
